title: SC EP:56 Sasquatch looking in the window
itunes:title: SC EP:56 Sasquatch looking in the window
description: Join us for a special mid-week show when we speak to an eye witness who has had a few encounters. One of the encounters he tells is when he was a young man and stared face to face with a Sasquatch. This is one show you will not want to miss. He goes into full details about what the face looked like at close range. Amazing encounter you will want to hear. We will also be giving you an update on our recent visit out to the Browns property!
